# 🏢 Multi-Tenant Domain-Adapted LLM Platform (POC)

An end-to-end, multi-tenant AI copilot platform demonstrating domain-specific fine-tuning, retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), preference alignment, and production MLOps.

This platform was built to prove scalable multi-tenancy: **One base model serving multiple isolated domains via dynamic PEFT (LoRA) adapter routing.**

## 🎯 Architecture Overview

![Multi-Tenant Architecture](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400.png?text=Architecture+Diagram+Here) *(Note: add a screenshot of a draw.io/Lucidchart diagram here if you make one)*

1. **Tenant A (SIS / Education):** Trained on student enrollment policies, FERPA guidelines, and attendance workflows.
2. **Tenant B (Manufacturing):** Trained on SOPs, defect classification, CAPA workflows, and safety protocols.

## ✨ Core Capabilities Implemented

- **Automated Data Curation Pipeline:** Ingests raw PDFs/docs, normalizes text, strips PII via regex rules, chunks for RAG, and auto-generates Instruction-Tuning (SFT) & Preference (DPO) datasets.
- **Cost-Efficient Multi-Tenancy:** Uses a single shared 4-bit quantized base model (`Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct`). Tenant-specific LoRA adapters are hot-swapped into VRAM at inference time based on the request's `tenant_id`.
- **Domain Alignment (SFT + DPO-lite):** Fine-tuned for domain terminology and aligned to refuse unsafe prompts (e.g., bypassing manufacturing safety, violating FERPA data privacy).
- **Isolated RAG & Grounding:** Separate Chroma vector indexes per tenant. Responses are strictly grounded with source citations to prevent hallucinations.
- **Observability & MLOps:** Integrated with MLflow for experiment tracking. SQLite-backed dashboard tracks latency, adapter canary splits, and usage metrics.
- **Omni-Channel Inference:** FastAPI streaming backend integrated with:
  - Next.js / Streamlit Web UI
  - Expo React Native Mobile Client
  - Python Voice Agent (Whisper STT -> LLM -> pyttsx3 TTS)

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **AI/ML:** PyTorch, Hugging Face (Transformers, PEFT, TRL, Accelerate), bitsandbytes
- **Data/RAG:** ChromaDB, Sentence-Transformers, pandas, pypdf
- **Backend:** FastAPI, Uvicorn, SSE (Server-Sent Events)
- **MLOps:** MLflow, SQLite, Streamlit
- **Voice:** faster-whisper, SpeechRecognition

